GIT REPO
Auto update README according to the comments at the beginning of the programs.
Thay way program authors write the README only once!

MINE7X7
Automatic empyting of items mined into chests, avoidance of iridium ore so that you can mine it yourself (this yielding 2 more ore!), communication to a central computer at your base on the status of the mining operation, etc.

DRILL4X4
Set the turtle to refuel itself when needed
